node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hay Day on July 02, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, food and text that says 'HAY DAY KITCHEN SUMMER ROLLS!'.

node.text:
[Link in Bio] We’re making Summer Rolls! 
A perfect and fresh, veggie-packed meal best enjoyed on hot Summer days!

We’ve prepared an easy recipe and a video, so you can follow along step-by-step.

Go ahead, give it a try!

#haydaykitchen

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hay Day on July 01, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text:
Farm Pass Season 8 has just started! We hope you all have a lot of fun! 🤩

Available this season:

New exclusive hat: Sand Cowboy Hat for your animals to wear!
Special Decoration #1: Hammock!
Special Decoration #2: Fitting Room!
Free Farm Pass perk: Extra Boat Help!
Free Decoration: Fish Fence!

Head over to your farm, tap on the new Baby Chick House- next to your neighborhood house,- and participate to receive all the great rewards! #FarmPass

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hay Day on June 30, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'HAY DAY VAllEY VALLEY The New season starting!'.

node.text:
A new Valley Season has started with a new exclusive decoration as the main reward!

🚨IMPORTANT 🚨We are working hard to fix the Android issues, We're preparing an optional update to resolve this to make sure everyone can play again! We're waiting for the update to be cleared and approved (this can take some time) . We apologize and thank you for the patience!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hay Day on June 28, 2021. May be a cartoon of 2 people and text that says 'HAY DAY M 25 Maggie Special!'.

node.text: Starting today, Maggie has some special birthday offers for you! Now’s a great time to give a new look to your house, truck and roadside shop!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hay Day on June 28, 2021. May be a cartoon of ‎text that says '‎HAY DAY مO Update Now!‎'‎.

node.text:
Our next FARMtastic update is here, just in time for summer! ☀🏖

Introducing a bigger farm and lots of new animals:

 • New farm expansion areas! Grow and decorate your dream farm even more!
 • Check out the special expansion areas with unique decorations!
 • New pet: we welcome our new Guinea Pig overlords!
 • New pet: Round out your stables with the new Appaloosa horse!
 • New sanctuary animals: the baby Reindeer are here!

Features & Improvements requested by YOU:

 • New production machine: Make a wide range of delicious donuts with the new donut maker. Yum!
 • Buy a second sugar mill to help with your sweet needs!
 • 9th birthday: New birthday products to celebrate! Cotton candy, colorfun candles and the birthday bouquet. Also stay tuned for new time-limited birthday customizations from Maggie!
• Love trains? Grab the new train track decoration from the Wheel of Fortune, and design your railroad path!
• Squashed loads of known bugs and issues.

#update #summer #hayday

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hay Day on June 26, 2021. May be a cartoon of 1 person and text that says 'HAY DAY 00 Animal Movies!'.

node.text:
What if your favorite animals were starring in your favorite movies? 🎥 What would be better the “Return of the MOOmmy“ or “The Pig Lebowsky”
Give us ideias for more movies in the comments!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hay Day on June 25, 2021. May be a cartoon of 2 people, food and text that says 'DAIRY NEWS'.

node.text:
Howdy Everyone!

[Link in Bio] A new episode of Dairy News is here! This episode is all about the new summer update and Hay Day's 9th Birthday. The update is packed with new content, such as new pets, a new production machine + products, new special Birthday products, new sanctuary animals, special Birthday Maggie customizations, new train tracks to decorate your farm and town... and more!

#update #dairynews #hayday
